Kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) muri rusange bwagendaga bwiyongera cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi.
Umubare w'abandura coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza imiterere imwe mu bihugu bigize EU/European Economic Area n'u Bwongereza, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi gikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu byose, nubwo kigenda gitandukana bitewe n'ibihugu.
Nk'uko byagezweho mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bikeneye kongera ubushishozi mu rwego rwo kwitegura ubwisungane mu kwivuza, cyane cyane mu kwivuza, mu gihe hari umubare munini w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu bataramenyekana bakekwaho indwara ya Samba mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyo mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko cyatewe na virusi ya corona nshya, yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yahawe izina ry'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibimenyetso bihari bigaragaza ko 80% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa butari bufite uburwayi bwo mu mahaha, kandi abenshi barakira.
14% by'abanduye kanseri, COVID-19 irushaho gukomera, igasaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro, naho 6% y'abanduye kanseri bakagira uburwayi bukomeye bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
4% by'abarwayi barwariye mu bitaro bapfuye bazira COVID-19.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugereranya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza n'intara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Ubu dutanze imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza, ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere ka Burayi k'Ubukungu n'u Bwongereza
COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa ikagera no mu tundi turere, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 ubu cyibasiye isi yose.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Spiteri et al. banditse ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020 mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Eurosurveillance 2020 bavuga ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemeje ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi, hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'uburwayi byatanzwe na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi, u Bufaransa ni bwo bwatangaje abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye tariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020, kandi abo bantu baturuka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bamaze kumenyekana mu bihugu 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe abarwayi 39,768 n'abapfuye 1,727 bari bamaze kumenyekana kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2020, muri bo 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441 bari mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kumenya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'ibyababayeho
Ibipimo by'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi byatangajwe n'Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) byaturutse gusa ku bikoresho byemewe n'amategeko, nk'ibiro bya Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, abategetsi b'ubuzima mu bihugu no mu turere na OMS, kandi bivugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/Area Ikigega cy'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza no kugereranya n'u Butaliyani.
Kubera ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ari ingenzi, twafashe iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 nk'ibyabaye, dukurikije imiterere ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Byongeye kandi, twatanze imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, tugereranyije n'iy'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/European Economic Area n'ibyateye imbere mu Bwongereza
Imimerere y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi n'Ubwongereza mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 yose, yakurikiwe n'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) muri rusange (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no ku Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho bugera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibitabo by'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abandura baturuka mu Butaliyani, ariko, ibindi bihugu bigize EU/European Economic Area n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje imiterere nk'iyo yo kwiyongera ku mubare w'abandura COVID-19 (ibikoresho by'ubufasha).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye urenze uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza.
Imimerere y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 yerekana ko icyorezo cyugarije isi kigenda gifata indi ntera mu bihugu byose.
Ibi biri kubera ko ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, hari itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'ubuzima bw'abaturage mu gihugu, kandi hari ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'imimerere n'amabwiriza mu bihugu bitandukanye mu guhitamo abarwayi bashobora gupimwa kugirango barebe ko COVID-19 iriho.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bihugu by'Ubutaliyani byibasiwe na virusi bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'abarwayi bitabwaho cyane muri ibyo bihugu byamaze kugera ku rwego rwo kwakira abarwayi.
Amakuru kuri COVID-19 avurwa mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye ubu ari kuri 6% na 1% by'abanduye mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'Uburayi (amakuru ntagaragara).
Ariko kandi, bagomba gukusanya amakuru mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo bashyigikire amakuru agezweho yo kugenzura, agaragaza umubare w'abamaze kwandura n'uw'abamaze gupfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-2011 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi, ibitanda byo kuvurwa cyane byari bitandukanye cyane n'ibisanzwe, biva kuri 29.2 mu Budage ku bantu 100.000, bikagera kuri 4.2 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira ububiko bw'ibitaro bingana cyangwa buciriritse ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda byo kuvurirwamo cyane n'iby'ubuvuzi bwo mu rwego rwo hagati ku bantu 100.000, mu 2010).
Ibipimo by'imiterere y'icyitegererezo bifitanye isano no guhuza ubushobozi bwo gufasha mu buvuzi, birenze 90 by'ibyago byo kugabanya ibitanda by'abarwayi bakomeye, ku mubare w'abandura COVID mu bitaro by'abarwayi buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, byatanzwe mu isesengura rya COVID-19 ryashyizweho na ECDC.
Kubera ko hari abantu benshi banduye muri EU/Afurika y'Igihugu cy'Ubukungu n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi by'indembe bikunze kwitabwaho n'abantu benshi, amakuru ku bantu banduye n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi by'indembe agomba gutangwa ku rwego rwa Statsis 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi cyihuta cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/umuryango w'ubukungu w'Uburayi ndetse no mu Bwongereza.
Niyo mpamvu, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bya hafi bigomba kwitegura, bazi ko SARS-CoV-2 izakomeza gukwirakwira mu baturage, kandi umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane cyane mu buvuzi bwa hafi, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe na virusi.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse rya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse kandi bufite intego bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2 ni ingenzi, kuva ku buryo bwo kugabanya indwara kugeza ku kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera kw'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu byitezwe ko bizagenda vuba mu gihe bidashyizweho mu gihe, bitazaha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no kumenyera uko bikora.
Gupima ibyago byihuse bigabanya ingamba z'ubuzima bw'abaturage zigamije kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Amasezerano y'ibihugu yo kongera ingamba zo kugabanya ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu rwego rwo kugabanya ingaruka ku buzima, nta gihe kinini afite.
Bitabaye ibyo, sisitemu z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu bigize EU/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi zizasuzugurika mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, zitewe n'abarwayi bakeneye kuvurwa.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 (Sars-CoV-2), cyibasiye abantu barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, ndetse cyahitanye abarenga 3.000.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura binyuze ku nyoni zo mu kirere, kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'iby'iyi virusi, ikaba ari na yo yateye SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu mwaka wa 2003.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse n'ubwandu buciriritse kurusha SARS, ariko igipimo cy'ubwandu kiruta kandi kibangamiye abagabo bakuze kurusha urubyiruko n'abagore.
Kubera ko umubare w'ibitabo byandikwa ku ndwara nshya wiyongera cyane, iyi nyandiko igerageza gutanga ubushakashatsi bwuzuye kandi bwuzuye ku mushinga w'ubushakashatsi wiyongera cyane.
Dushyira ahagaragara ingingo z'ibanze z'ibyorezo, iby'indwara, iby'ubwandu, uburyo bwo kubimenya, uburyo bwo kuvurwa no kwirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzafasha gusobanukirwa no kwirinda indwara iteje akaga.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wari urimo ibintu bitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose, kubera ko Abashinwa bari baburiwe ko batagomba kuva mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'uwo munsi mukuru no nyuma yawo, kubera icyorezo gishya cy'ubwandu.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (COV) yatumye habaho indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka mu mwaka wa 2003, bityo ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa COVID-19.
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyihuse mu gihugu hose kigera mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wari warenze 80.000, abarwayi barenga 40.000 baramaze kuva mu bitaro, abasaga 3,000 barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi w'abaturage wa mbere kandi ko ishobora kwangiza byinshi kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko tubikesha PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri kuva raporo ya mbere yasohoka ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 200 ku bijyanye na COVID-19, harimo n'ibya virusi, indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara z'ubwandu, indwara z'indwara n'ubuvuzi, zigena urutonde rw'ubwandu bwa virusi zatoranyijwe mu barwayi batandukanye.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugamije gusobanura mu magambo make ibyo umuntu yabonye mu bushakashatsi ku ngingo nshya ihinduka mu buryo bwihuse.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na COVID, indwara yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyo mu 2012).
Tuzasuzuma ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kumenya amateka yayo, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo bikomeje ariko byihutirwa.
CoVs, ubusanzwe zibonwa nk'indwara zitera urupfu ku bantu, ni zo zitera ibicurane bigera kuri 15%.
Ariko kandi, muri iki kinyejana twahuye n'indwara zikomeye z'ubwandu inshuro ebyiri (SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV), bwa mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, nyuma y'aho zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi mu buryo bwihuse, zigateza indwara n'urupfu bikabije.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV cyanditswe mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1, abantu batangiye kwandura indwara ya Samba bataramenyekana aho yaturutse, babimenyesheje Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya Covid cyakomeje.
Tariki 15 Mutarama 2020, urupfu rwa mbere rwanditswe mu mazi.
Hagati aho, iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu bihugu by'ibituranyi no mu bindi bihugu.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abashinzwe ubuzima batangaje ko hari abantu banduye iyi virusi, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ishobora kwandura umuntu ku wundi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, imodoka zose z'abaturage zahagaritse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi umujyi wose warafunze.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwakozwe ku wa 24 Mutarama ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko ku barwayi 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye isano ya bugufi n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu mazi, aho bivugwa ko bituruka ku matungo atazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku isi.
