Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihuse yo gusuzuma no kuvura icyorezo cya 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV), kandi aya mabwiriza atanga ubunararibonye bwacu kandi atanga icyerekezo cyiza cyo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Nyamara, Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, kandi ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro binyuze mu bushakashatsi bukomeje no mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi, bityo, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura bukomeje kuba hafi.
Muri iyi baruwa, twasubije ibitekerezo byacu ku mabwiriza kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya by'igenzura bishingiye ku mabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (Igitabo cya karindwi) nk'uko byatangajwe n'akanama gashinzwe ubuzima rusange ka Repubulika ya Rubanda y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya (2019-nCoV), ubu cyitwa ku mugaragaro indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi yitwa syndrome respiratoire grave coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize COVID-19 mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo ku isi.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze amabwiriza yihuse kandi asohoka kuri interineti ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020 mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare.
Kuva yasohoka, abantu benshi barayishishikaje.
Ariko kandi, wibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, kandi ko ubushakashatsi n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi bishingiye ku byo tumaze kubona, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro, bityo uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura na bwo bugenda buhinduka.
