Amateka y'indwara: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu nkengero zawo, aho havuzwe ko hari abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara bitangira, cyangwa amateka y'ingendo cyangwa kuba mu bindi bice bya COVID-19, (2) amateka y'abahuye n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bifashijwemo na aluminium acid test), (3) amateka y'abahuye n'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu ifitanye isano na COVID-19, (4) urutonde rw'abantu banduye (≥ 2K) mu byumweru 2 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'indwara bitangira, mu bice by'abantu banduye (urugero: mu ngo, mu biro, mu kazi, n'ahandi).
Imiterere y'abaganga: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso by'ibanze byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'amaraso yera ugaragaza imibare isanzwe, yagabanutse cyangwa yagabanutse y'ibinyabuzima by'amaraso mu gihe cy'icyiciro cya mbere.
Gupima icyemezo cyemejwe bigomba gushingira ku kibazo gikekwaho: 1) gupima PCR yigihe nyacyo ya SARS-CoV-2; (2) gukurikira kwa virusi yose yerekana ko ifite ubushobozi bwo kwanduza virusi nshya ya corona; (3) gupima serumu ku buryo bwihariye IgM anti-human na IgG anti-human SARS-CoV-2 mu iseri, cyangwa kuva ku buryo bwihariye IgG SARS-CoV-2 antibody igaragara ko idafite, cyangwa ihinduka ry'ibice birenga 4 mu gihe cyo gukira nyuma yo gukira.
