Ikoreshwa ry'ijambo social distancing ryerekeza ku bantu bagomba kwiherera mu buryo bwuzuye, aho kuba inama yo gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo. Bamwe mu bayobozi batanze amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere akoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Muri byo harimo no kugisha inama abantu ko baryamana gusa n'umuntu babana kandi udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19 basabwa kuguma mu rugo bakajya kwiherera.
Inzego z'ubuzima zatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwitandukanya. Leta nyinshi zasabye abantu bari mu turere twugarijwe na virusi kwitandukanya.
Amabwiriza akomeye yo kwitarura abandi yahawe abantu bari mu matsinda y'abari mu kaga gakomeye.
Abantu bashobora kuba bagaragarijwe n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 ndetse n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere ka virusi bagirwa inama yo kwigunga mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye ku munsi wa nyuma w'igaragaza.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura ikwirakwira ryayo ni ukubuza cyangwa gukumira no kugabanya.
Gufunga ibikorwa bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, bigamije kumenyekanisha ubundi buryo bushya bwo kugenzura ubwandu mu rwego rwo kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye no kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu baturage.
Niba ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ridashobora guhagarikwa, ibizamini bizakurikirwa no gufata ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira no guhangana n'ingaruka ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Ingamba zo gufata no kurwanya indwara zishobora gufatirwa hamwe.
Kugira ngo icyorezo cy'indwara zandura kigabanuke ku kigero kiri munsi ya 1, hakenewe ingamba zikomeye kurushaho. Kimwe mu bintu byo kurwanya icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya icyorezo cy'indwara hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, buzwi nka "icyorezo cy'icyorezo".
Ibi bizatuma haboneka igihe gihagije cyo gutegura inkingo n'ubuvuzi, bityo bigatuma abashinzwe ubuzima badasabwa gukora cyane.
Ingamba zo kwirinda zirimo kwirinda ibiyobyabwenge bishobora kugabanya icyorezo, harimo isuku y'amaboko, gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru no kwitandukanya n'abandi; ingamba zo mu rwego rw'imibereho yo kwirinda guhagarara kure, nko gufunga amashuri, guhagarika gahunda zo guteranira hamwe; gushishikariza abaturage kugira uruhare mu gushyiraho ingamba zo kubahiriza ibyo bibujijwe, no gukora isuku. Mu Bushinwa, mu gihe icyorezo cyari cyamaze kugera ku rwego rwo hejuru, ingamba zo kugabanya icyorezo zafashwe mu buryo bwimbitse.
Ibihugu byinshi byateye intambwe zitandukanye mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bwo gupima no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi itanga itangazo iyo abantu banduye bari mu bikorwa.
Singapore yongeye guhana abakoze ibyo mu gihe yari imaze gutanga inkunga ku bantu bari bamaze igihe biherereye mu bwigunge.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa no gutanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'u Bwongereza na Amerika bugaragaza ko hari ibibazo bikomeye byo kugabanya (kugabanya icyorezo ariko ntihagire icyakwirakwira) no kucyirinda (guhindura icyorezo).
Gushyiraho politiki z'ubuvuzi zihuje n'igihe, bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa ku kigero cya 2/3 cy'abanduye, ariko umubare w'abapfa mu bihumbi n'uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima, bigaragaza ko hari ibindi bibazo.
Mu gihe virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu, birashoboka ko hakoreshwa uburyo bwo guhagarika, ariko bigomba gutegereza (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzabonekera, niba ari rwo rwa mbere), kuko igihe cyose bibaye ngombwa, ikwirakwira rizongera vuba.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo gukumira iki cyorezo bizatuma habaho ibibazo by'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yihariye ya COVID-19 yemewe, ariko nta bikorwa byo guteza imbere birimo no gusuzuma imiti iriho.
Gufata imiti, kunywa ibinyobwa n'ikiruhuko bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Ukurikije uburemere bw'umubiri, umuntu ashobora gukenera imiti ya ogisijeni, imiti yo gutera amaraso no gufashwa guhumeka.
Gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ingaruka zikomeye kurushaho.
Ibigo byinshi byemewe kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi birimo gusuzumwa mu bijyanye no kuvura COVID-19.
"Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze ko hari ""imiti gakondo n'imiti ikorerwa mu rugo"" ishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-19".
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 no kunoza ubuvuzi ari ingamba z'ibanze zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ibiro by'akarere by'u Burayi bya ECDC na OMS byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'imirimo y'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze harimo kwibanda ku serivisi za laboratwari zo gupima COVID-19, guhagarika uburyo igihe cyose bishoboka, kumenya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi bafite COVID-19 no gutoza abakozi kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bakomeye no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka n'ibitanda bihari.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi bivuga ku birebana n'inkomoko y'ikintu cya mbere (umurwayi wa ziro).
Umuntu wa mbere wafashwe na coronavirus yavumbuwe ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wagabanutse buhoro buhoro.
Byinshi muri byo byari bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Havana ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, uretse kugurisha inyamaswa zibayeho, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yaturutse kuri imwe muri izi nyamaswa, cyangwa se mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
"Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan babwiye bagenzi babo ko basanze "virusi ya corona imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani, harimo na Li Wenliang, bahawe igihano na polisi kubera ko bakwirakwizaga amakuru y'ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, ahabwa igihano n'umuyobozi we kubera ko yakwirakwizaga amakuru y'ibinyoma.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan nyuma yo gutanga itangazo ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza yamenyesheje OMS.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima muri Wuhan babwiwe ko hari abantu benshi bafite indwara ya pneumonia itaramenyekana, kugira ngo basuzumwe mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro na hagati ya Mutarama 2020, kuba igihugu cy'Ubushinwa ari ikigo cy'ingendo n'ingendo nyuma y'umwaka mushya, hamwe n'ibigo bikomeye by'ingendo za gari ya moshi, byafashije virusi gukwirakwira mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe muri Shenzhen.
Nyuma y'aho, amakuru yemewe agaragaza ko kugeza ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu 6.174 bagaragaje ibimenyetso. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zarengeye u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani mu mubare w'abamaze kwandura. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose, abantu barenga miriyoni 1.61 bari bamaze kwandura, abasaga 97.000 barapfuye, abasaga 364.000 barakira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere nibura bifite umuntu umwe wanduye.
Ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byatangiye kugenzura imipaka kubera icyorezo cyateye mu Burayi, bibuza urujya n'uruza rw'abantu.
Ingamba z'igihugu zirimo guhagarika abantu gutaha, guhagarika abantu gutaha, no guhagarika ingendo. Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abaturage bagera kuri miliyoni 300 cyangwa 90% by'abaturage muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bari mu bihe by'imihango yo gutaha, miliyoni 50 muri Filipine, miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo, na miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu bagera kuri miriyari 1.7 bari mu mazu cyangwa mu bindi bice byayo, bakaba bariyongereye bava kuri miliyari 2 ku muntu umwe bagera kuri miriyari 2.6.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 yabonetse ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, raporo itari yemewe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere yabonetse ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yabonye icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, hanyuma ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, A.A. yabibwiye ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Wuhan Jianghan CDC.
Ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, ibipimo by'imiterere y'umubiri byerekanye ko hari virusi ya corona isa na SARS.
Itangazo ry'umwanzuro ryashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umutungo wa Huang ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryabitangaje kuri uwo munsi.
Mu gihe ibyo bitangazo byabaga, abapolisi bari baragabishije abaganga bo mu mazi ko batangaga "Alubalata".
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yavuze ko nta gihamya ifatika y'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura undi muntu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye bwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi, nk'uko Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, yabivuze.
Mu gihe cyiswe "igitaramo gikomeye kurusha ibindi byose mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, hakozwe gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo zo mu mazi, mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite mu mujyi birabujijwe.
Umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) wahagaritswe mu bihugu byinshi.
Abayobozi b'icyo gihugu batangaje ko ibitaro by'agateganyo byitwa Huashenshan Hospital bizubakwa mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hakurikiyeho kubaka ibitaro byitwaga Leschenshun kugira ngo haboneke abarwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibigo 14 by'umwihariko nka pariki rusange na sitade muri Wuhan, mu bitaro bya gisikare. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe izindi ngamba zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutangaza itangazo rishya n'itangazo ku bantu batwara abantu no kongera iminsi mikuru yihariye.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu ntara byafunzwe.
Mu bice bya Hong Kong na Macau, ingamba nyinshi zagiye zikorwa, cyane cyane ku mashuri na kaminuza.
Mu turere twinshi tw'Ubushinwa, ingamba zo gukora kure zatangiye gushyirwa mu bikorwa.
Imipaka yo gutembera mu mujyi wa Hubei no hanze yaryo iracyariho.
Muri u Bushinwa, amazu ndangamurage yafunzwe by'agateganyo kubera ko hahindutse uburyo bwo gutwara abantu.
"Kugenzura urujya n'uruza rw'abaturage byashyizwe mu bikorwa mu mijyi myinshi, bituma abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage bose b'Ubushinwa) bahatirwa kuguma mu ngo zabo. Nyuma y'uko ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo rigeze ku rwego mpuzamahanga muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira virusi "kwinjira"" mu Bushinwa ivuye mu bindi bihugu".
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo gufungira abanyamahanga mu kigo cyateguriwe abimukira. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa, habaye ikibazo cya Ndze gusa, cyabaye mu minsi itanu ishize, bitewe n'uko umuntu wari uvuye i Istanbul yaje mu gikapu cye.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ubwandu bwo mu gihugu bwahagaritswe kandi ko ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo mu Bushinwa ryafashwe.
Ku munsi w'ejo, amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo muri Hubei yarorohejwe, mu mezi abiri nyuma yo guhagarika ingendo hanze ya Wuhan. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko abantu bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura mu gihugu batazashobora kwinjira kuva ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko ntiharatangazwa igihe iryo tegeko rizasubirwamo.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yashyizeho ingamba zo gufasha ubucuruzi n'inganda bitandukanye byafunzwe kubera COVID-19 gusubira mu bikorwa byabyo kuva ku ya 21 Werurwe 2012, kandi yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga yo gutera inkunga no gukangurira izi nzego. Nubwo bihuza n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming wizihizwa buri mwaka, abayobozi b'igihugu batangaje ko tariki ya 26 Werurwe 2012 saa yine ari umunsi wo kurira ku rwego rw'igihugu, kandi basabye iminota 3 yo gusenga. Leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye abaturage kwitabwaho no gushyiraho gahunda yo kwirinda COVID-19 kugira ngo itazongera kuboneka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, COVID-19 yatanzwe nk'inkuru y'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cyaturutse mu Bushinwa kigera muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habonetse ubwandu bwinshi, ahanini bitewe n'amateraniro mu idini rishya rya Daegu rizwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Gusura kwa Shincheonji i Wuhan byateye inkeke ko bishobora kuba byaratumye ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare 2020, mu bayoboke 9,336 bari muri kiliziya, abagera kuri 13% bari bafite ibimenyetso 1,261. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ari mu bihe by'ubutagondwa ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abamaze kwandura barenga 2.000, ku ya 29 Mutarama bari bageze ku 3150.
Abasirikare batatu banduye virusi, inkambi zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zagiye mu kato.
Porogaramu z'indege nazo zarabangamiwe, bityo zarahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje gahunda nini kandi iteguye kurusha izindi ku isi yo kugenzura abaturage kugira ngo bamenye abantu bose banduye, kandi ishakishe kandi itandukane n'abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura burimo kwemeza by'agateganyo ibimenyetso by'indwara ku bantu bashya binjira ku isi binyuze kuri porogaramu igendanwa, gupima virusi mu modoka aho ibisubizo bizatangazwa ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20.000 ku munsi.
Nubwo gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo itakomeje gufunga imijyi yose, yagaragaje ko ifite imbaraga mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bakoze ibikorwa byo gukusanya imikono basaba Perezida Moon ko yakurikiranwa cyangwa bashimira igisubizo cye kubera ko leta itari yafashe neza icyorezo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ko hari umuntu umwe wafashwe ku munsi, mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bine.
Kuva ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe kugeza ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya binjira mu gihugu bazajya bafatwa mu byiciro by'abimukira mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru agaragaza ko kugeza ku itariki ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yasabye ibihugu 121 gufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje icyorezo cya mbere cya SARS-CoV-2 mu mujyi wa Quwe ku ya 19 Gashyantare, nkuko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuzima, abantu babiri bapfuye kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba zafashwe na leta zirimo gufunga ibitaramo n'andi materaniro y'umuco, imikino, imihango yo ku wa gatanu, kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri abanza n'amashuri yisumbuye.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari eshanu za Rials mu kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yatangaje kuwa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gufunga ahantu hatandukanye hatangajwe ko hazabaho ubwandu, ko ahubwo abantu bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Nubwo imodoka nyinshi zikomeje kugendana hagati y'imijyi mbere ya Nourouz y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi, muri Werurwe hatangajwe gahunda yo guhagarika urujya n'uruza rw'imijyi.
Ahantu hatagatifu h'Abashia i Qouq hagiye haguma hagaragara ku bantu bakora ingendo zo mu buryo bw'umwuka kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu kuvuga ku byaha byo guhishira cyane icyorezo cya Iran, ibihugu birenga icumi bihuza ibihugu byabo na Irani ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko hashobora kuba hari ikwirakwira rikomeye kurusha abarwayi 388 batangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, nyuma y'uko 23 mu bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko 290 basuzumwe basanga bafite virusi.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani gufungura by'agateganyo abafunzwe bahora baharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu, no gufungura by'agateganyo abantu bose bafunzwe mu buryo bukwiriye.
Ibigo by'ubuvuzi by'abashomeri, nk'amabohero, ni byo bifite ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi, aho usanga nta bufasha buhagije bw'ubuvuzi buboneka.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Iran n'abari abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara ku ya 17 Werurwe 2020.
Tariki 23 Werurwe, Irani ifite abantu bashya 50 banduye coronavirus buri saha, naho buri minota icumi hapfa umuntu umwe.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Iran ishobora kuba ifite abantu bakubye inshuro eshanu abo imaze kwandura.
Yavuze ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kwangiza ubushobozi bw'igihugu mu bijyanye n'imari mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komisiyo nkuru y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byashyizweho ku bihugu byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani, bikurwaho.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bageragereshwaga SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Leta y'Ubutaliyani yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu, ihagarika by'agateganyo ingendo z'indege ziva mu Bushinwa zijya mu Butaliyani, ndetse n'izova mu Butaliyani zijya mu Bushinwa, kubera ko umubare w'abandura wiyongereye mu gihe gito.
Kuva ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, mu karere ka Lombardy, habonetse abantu 16 banduye, icyiciro cy'abanduye COVID-19 nacyo cyongeye kugaruka. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, inama y'abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo kugenzura ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 mu mirenge 11 itandukanye mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko nta muntu uzinjira cyangwa ngo asohoke mu turere dufite icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, ubwo umubare w'abapfuye mu Butaliyani wageraga ku 100, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose.
Ibirori byose by'imikino, harimo imikino ya Serie A, byari biteganyijwe ko bizaba mu minsi ya Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, siporo zose zahagaritswe byibura ukwezi kose.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarara hafi aho usibye amaduka manini n'amavuriro. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'ubuvuzi, ubuvuzi, guhugura no kwita ku barwayi (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama z'imyitwarire y'ubuvuzi ku mabwiriza yo kugenzura mu bihe by'ibiza.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatanze raporo y'abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize icyorezo cya coronavirus, nyuma yo gutsinda Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda za gisirikare zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
