Ibizamini bya laboratwari bikoresha uburyo bwo kumenya indwara ya coronavirus yo mu kirere 2019 (COVID-19) hamwe na virusi ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 hamwe na za antibodies zisubiza iyi ndwara.
Virusi mu bipimo by'amaraso byemezwa na RT-PCR, ishobora kumenya RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki cyuma kirimo ubushobozi buke kandi gishobora gufasha mu kumenya SARS-CoV-2.
Ibyo bifasha kumenya niba hari indwara ziherutse kwandura cyangwa niba hari izindi zigeze kwandura.
Igikorwa cyo gupima udukoko tw'ubumara (serology) ni ingirakamaro mu gupima no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'umubare w'abantu bafite ibimenyetso ariko bakavuga ko nta bimenyetso bafite cyangwa badafite.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu n'ubushobozi bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri by'abantu benshi bishobora kumenyekana binyuze muri iki kizamini.
Kubera ubushakashatsi buciriritse, nta gihugu na kimwe gifite amakuru y'ukuri ku byerekeye uko icyorezo cyakwirakwijwe mu baturage muri Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi ibizamini bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Ibyo bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, kubera ko mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe usanga imibare y'abapfa iruta kure cyane iya mbere.
Ikoranabuhanga ryo gusuzuma mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga (rRT-PCR) ry'igihe gito, rituma umuntu ashobora gusuzuma urugero rw'ibisukari cyangwa icyuma.
Ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi ibiri.
Ibipimo bya RT-PCR bifata urugero rw'umunyu mu muhogo, bifatwa nk'ibiringirwa mu cyumweru cya mbere gusa cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo ikongera ikaza mu gitsina.
Ku bantu banduye bamaze icyumweru cya kabiri bagenzurwa, uburyo bushobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma ni uburyo bwo gufata urugero rw'umwimerere (urugero) cyangwa uburyo bwo gufata urugero (urugero) mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero.
Imwe mu mashini ya mbere ya PCR yatangijwe i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020, ikorwa na Charité.
Ubwongereza bwateguye ibizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cyitwa Kogenebiotech cyateguye igikoresho cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
"Buri gihe, ikigo cya BGI mu Bushinwa ni cyo cya mbere cyabonye inkunga yihutirwa y'ubuyobozi bw'ibikoresho by'ubuzima mu Bushinwa, kikaba ari igikoresho gishingiye kuri PCR cyo kumenya SARS-CoV-2. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura no kwirinda indwara (CDC) kiri gutanga icyiciro cya 2019 cya coronavirus nshya (2019-nCoV) mu gihe cy'igerageza rya RT-PCR mu bigo nderabuzima byo mu karere, binyuze mu bikoresho by'ubuyobozi mpuzamahanga".
Mu bipimo bitatu by'ibanze, ibisubizo bitari byo byatewe no kubura ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ibanze mu bikoresho bya kera byo gupima, kandi byateje impaka ku gupima kwa CDC i Atlanta, aho ibipimo 100 ku munsi byakozwe neza mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, nta cyemezo cyemejwe cy'uko ibipimo bikoreshwa mu byiciro bibiri byemewe, kandi kugeza ubu, ibizamini by'igihugu n'ibyaho ntibyemerewe gukora.
Iki kizamini cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti, mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, mu gihe cy'ikoreshwa ry'ibiza. Ibigo by'ubushakashatsi by'ubucuruzi muri Amerika byatangiye gukora ibizamini mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko hari icyiciro cy'igihugu cy'igerageza rya COVID-19 rishingiye kuri RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics yateguye ibizamini bya COVID-19 ku rwego rw'igihugu ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mubare ntarengwa usobanutse, ariko isuzuma no gutunganya ibipimo bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyateguwe kandi kigakorwa na VECTOR, ikigo cya leta gishinzwe ubushakashatsi mu by'imikorere y'agakoko gatera indwara n'ikoranabuhanga mu binyabuzima.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko yateguye ibizamini byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ibizamini byinshi cyane bivuga ibisubizo mu masaha 3.5, byemerera ibizamini 4,128 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa ry'ibanze (EUA) muri Laboratwari za Abbott, ikoresha uburyo bwa Abbott m2000, kandi FDA yahaye ibyangombwa nk'ibyo Hologic, LabCorp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid yabonye EUA imwe na FDA, kandi ifite iminota 45.
