Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ubu hari imashini zigera ku 18.000, kandi Abbott iri kwihutisha ibikorwa byo gukora ibizamini bigera ku 50.000 ku munsi. Ikizamini gikoresha umuti urwanya virusi ya corona (N-proteine) kizajya gihuza by'ukuri na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (N-proteine), kandi byitezwe ko kizajya kigaragaza ibisubizo mu minota 15 cyangwa 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo byihuse bya grippe.
