Ibimenyetso bisanzwe kuri CT harimo opasifiti z'ibirahuri by'ubwoko bubiri, hamwe n'ibisate by'inyuma.
Iyo indwara ihindutse, usanga abantu batandukanye cyane, batagira gahunda, kandi ntibabona ibintu mu buryo bushyize mu gaciro.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko PCR mu mazi y'ibanze igereranywa na CT, igaragaza ko CT ari yo ikora neza kurusha PCR, ariko ko ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gufata amashusho, kandi ko ibyinshi mu bintu by'ibanze biboneka mu mashusho ari kimwe n'iby'indwara z'ibicurane n'uburwayi.
