Ariko isabune n'amazi ni byo bikora neza kurusha imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 y'ibicurane A na Clostridium difficile ku ntoki. Mu bigo nderabuzima, kugira ngo haboneke ubuziranenge mu ntoki, hashobora kuba harimo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera gahunda yo gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe inzoga, no guha abakozi amabwiriza yanditse n'ayanditse.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse kugira ngo hamenyekane uburyo bwo kuvura bufite akamaro mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifatwa nk'uburyo bwo kugabanya amafaranga, kugira ubuzima bwiza no kugira ibyokurya byiza.
Ariko kandi, kubura amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, mu mashuri no ku kazi, bituma kugera ku mahame mpuzamahanga yo gukaraba intoki bitoroha.
Urugero, nubwo hari uburyo bworoshye bwo kubaka aho bakarabirira intoki, muri Afurika yo mu cyaro hafi ya hose, nta byumba byo gukarabirira intoki biboneka hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa rusange.
Ariko kandi, kuba abantu bakoresha amazi make mu gihe bakaraba intoki, bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko hari imico runaka.
Guteza imbere no kwigisha gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki, kongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abaturage bagira ihinduka rirambye mu myitwarire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikorwe neza, ni ngombwa kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi 70 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bwo kwiyuhagira mu baturage bwagize akamaro mu kongera umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki mu bigo by'amashuri, ariko ko gahunda zo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga nta cyo zigeze zigeraho. Urugero rumwe ni uburyo bwa UNICEF bw'inyenyeri eshatu, bushishikariza abanyeshuri gufata ingamba zoroshye kandi zidahenze zo gukaraba intoki n'isabune, mu bindi bintu by'isuku.
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byujuje, amashuri ashobora kuzamuka agera ku nyenyeri imwe cyangwa eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Urundi rugero ni ubukangurambaga bwo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose bugamije guhindura imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus cyo mu mwaka wa 2019-2020, UNICEF yashishikarije gukwirakwiza emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwibanda ku ngaruka rusange zo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere bijyanye na DALY.
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo by'ingenzi kurusha andi mabwiriza arebana n'amazi n'isuku.
Igikoresho cy'ibanze cy'ubuvuzi bw'amaboko cyatangijwe mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abahanga babiri mu by'isuku y'amaboko: Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umuhungari wakoraga i Vienne muri Hongiriya, na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza washinze ubuforomo bwo mu gihe cya none.
Icyo gihe abantu benshi batekerezaga ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi y'ibinure.
