Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19
Igenzura ry'ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ryemeza ko ingamba zo kwirinda mu kazi ari zo z'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago by'akazi bizaba ngombwa bizaterwa n'aho umuntu akorera ndetse n'ubwoko bw'akazi akora, hagendewe ku buryo umuntu ashobora kwandura COVID-19, aho ashobora kwandurira mu baturage n'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi (OSHA) kivuga ko akazi gafite ibyago bike ari akazi gafite aho umuntu ahurira n'abandi ndetse n'abandi bakorana, aho hakenewe ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, nko gukaraba intoki, abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka no gukomeza isuku isanzwe no kwirinda kwandura.
