Ibyo bikubiyemo abantu baba mu gace batuyemo, urugero nk'abanyeshuri, abantu baba mu duce dufite abantu benshi n'abantu baba mu maduka manini.
Mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago by'iki cyiciro, hakurikijwe ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, umuntu agomba kuba afite uburyo bwo guhumeka bukoresha uburyo bwo guhanagura umwuka cyane, ndetse n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abantu bafite ibyago bikomeye byo kwandura COVID-19 ku muntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba yarayanduye, bafite ibyago byinshi cyane iyo abakozi bakusanya ibipimo by'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19 mu gihe bakora ibikorwa byo gutangiza mu kirere.
Ku bantu nk'abo, uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago buhuje n'ubuhanga, urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bigabanya umuvuduko w'umwuka, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bya bwite bikenewe mu kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi barirukanwa ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi no gutinya ko bashobora kurwara.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, hakubiyemo n'ibyo abantu bakeneye n'uko babibona (byaba mu gihe cy'amasaha adahagije cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga ibyokurya cyangwa mu modoka).
