Hariho gahunda z'akazi zifitanye isano n'aho bakorera ndetse n'uburyo bakorera, aho usanga hari ibyago, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, ndetse n'ibyago byugarije buri mukozi ufite imyaka myinshi n'uburwayi bukomeye.
Nanone kandi, basuzuma uburyo bwo kwirinda izo ngaruka, n'uburyo bwo kwirinda icyorezo.
