Kugira ngo duhindure imikorere yacu nshya n'amasaha y'akazi ya buri munsi, tugomba guhindura igihe gahunda yacu y'umwaka ya 2020-2021 izarangirira.
Intego yacu ni ugusaba ko gahunda yacu ya 2019-2020 yakongerwa, bityo abakozi bagashobora gukora imirimo isaba, kwibeshaho, kwita ku miryango yabo, kandi ibyo bigakemura ibibazo by'abashaka gukora amasaha make.
Iyo ndunduro y'igihe igabanya cyane imihangayiko n'imihangayiko byo muri gahunda muri iki gihe ku rwego rw'umuryango wose.
Mu cyumweru gitaha tuzabwira abakozi bacu inama, hanyuma abahagarariye n'amatsinda tubamenyeshe icyiciro gikurikira, vuba vuba amakuru amaze gutangwa.
Turabashimira ubuyobozi mwatanze muri iki gihe, mu itsinda rya APP.
Mu by'ukuri, iyo umuntu ari mu biro, aba afite umutekano, kandi aba afite isuku.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twamenye ko umwe mu bo dukorana bashinze SF ashobora kuba yaranduye virusi ya COVID-19.
Ariko, kubera ko dufite amakenga, twashyizeho abakozi bo kurwanya virusi mu biro byacu by'i San Francisco.
Buri gisenge bakigize kitagira ubwandu bakoresheje uburyo bwo kurwanya virusi bukoreshwa mu bitaro, harimo n'aho bakirira n'ibiro by'abazamura imodoka bigera ku gisenge cyacu.
Inzu ifite uburyo bwayo bwo kwita ku nyubako ikoresha ibicuruzwa byayo bigamije kurinda umutekano w'abahatuye.
Twiringiye ko igihe tuzaba dufashe umwanzuro wo gusubira mu biro, bizakorwa mu buryo bwuzuye.
Ibiro bya DC biri muri WeWork, kandi batanze amakuru yabo kuri COVID-19 kuri twe n'abakozi bacu muri DC.
Mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu byo muri Washington DC byakurikije amabwiriza ya San Francisco ku buryo byashoboraga gukorerwa imirimo yose ivuye mu rugo.
Nkuko bamwe mu bakozi bacu bo muri NYC babizi, turimo no kuganira ku bijyanye no gukodesha ikibanza i Brooklyn.
Ibi biganiro byarakomeje ariko bishobora gutinda.
Bamwe mu bakozi bacu ni ubwa mbere bakorera mu rugo.
Abakozi bacu bamaze igihe kirekire mu kazi, bazi ko bishobora kuba ari uguhuza, kandi bashaka kuguha inama:
Jya ukoresha neza igihe cyawe, kandi ujye ukoresha neza igihe cyawe.
Niba ukeneye igihe kirekire, tekereza uko wakora ngo ugire icyo ugeraho mu gihe cy'iminsi myinshi.
Sobanura neza iby'amateraniro, ugire gahunda, kandi uheruke kohereza ibitabo byo gusoma.
Gushyira videwo mu buryo bwibanze, harimo ibikoresho nka Google Docs na Zoom, byorohereza ubufatanye n'ubufatanye butaziguye.
Jya ugira umuntu uyobora buri teraniro, usuzume ibiganiro, usuzume urutonde rw'abavuga, kandi umufashe gufata inyandiko (cyangwa ujye ufata inyandiko ufatanyije n'abandi).
Niba ukeneye indangururamajwi nziza, andikira ubufasha bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Ujye ukoresha amafaranga y'ubwishingizi mu manza.
Andika kuri #remoties kugira ngo uganire n'abo mukorana ku mirimo yanyu
Itsinda ry'abakozi ririmo gushakisha uburyo bwo gukora akazi gakwirakwizwa muri Fondasiyo binyuze mu gutanga ubuyobozi bwa Ergonomics bushingiye kuri webinar.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twasabye abitabiriye inkunga y'umuryango guhagarika ibikorwa by'ikigega Wikimedia, nk'ibya Editatons, kugeza igihe OMS izaba ivuze ko icyorezo cyarangiye.
Bongeyeho ko nta muntu uhanwa kubera gutinda cyangwa guhindura intego, kuko bumva ko gusaba ko bavanwaho bishobora gutuma batarangira amasezerano y'ubufasha bari baragiranye.
Mu cyumweru gitaha, tuzakomeza gutanga ibitekerezo kuri Wikimania no ku yindi nama y'akarere n'iy'abaturage.
Imyitwarire y'umuryango mpuzamahanga ntabwo ari agahinda gusa, ahubwo ni n'ibyishimo biturutse ku myifatire y'ubushishozi yo kwita ku muryango wabo bwite, Wikimedia n'abandi kubera imvururu zabayeho.
Mu gihe kiri imbere, CRT irimo gukora ku buryo hashyirwaho urubuga rwa Meta-Wiki, kugira ngo rushobore kugabanya igitutu ku baturage no gukomeza gukorana nabo.
