Catherine ni umwe mu bagize CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, na Tony S), hamwe n'itsinda ry'abayobozi (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M, na Toby N).
b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo iboneka mu bice by'inyuma by'ingirabuzimafatizo (membrane) zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ni umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'amaraso, kuko igabanya ingano ya angogletin-II kandi ikongera Ang (1-7), igahagarika ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura ingirabuzima fatizo (ACE). ACE2 ikoreshwa nk'inzira yinjira mu ngirabuzima fatizo zimwe na zimwe za coronavirus.
Iyo enzyme iboneka mu bantu, akenshi yitwa hACE2.
Ingirozitini-enzymes 2 ni ingirozitini irimo ibyuma (ironloenzyme) iboneka mu bice by'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ishyirwa mu cyiciro cya N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal collectrin cy'indwara z'impyiko z'indwara z'impyiko.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bwa mbere bw'umushongi wanduza, kuko iyi enzyme ifite urubuga rw'umushongi, kandi iboneka ku gifu no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
ACE2 ikurwa mu gice cy'inyuma cy'ingirabuzimafatizo n'ikindi kimenyetso cyitwa shidas, maze ikurwamo poroteyine isohoka mu maraso, amaherezo ikajya mu cyondo.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata cyane cyane ingirabuzimafatizo z'uruhu rwa alveolar type II, mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, mu maraso mato, mu maraso no mu mitsi, no mu maraso.
ACE2 mRNA iboneka mu gice cy'uruti rw'umugongo, mu gice cy'uruti rw'umugongo, mu gice cy'uruti rw'umugongo no mu bice by'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni ugushyira mu gaciro ku birebana na ACE.
ACE ikora angiotensin I ikora angiotensin II ikora mu buryo bugabanya amaraso.
ACE2 nayo ifata amino acide yitwa phenylalanine, ari yo ihererekanya imitsi y'ibinyabutabire, ikava mu bwoko bwa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe), ikajya mu bwoko bwa angiotestine (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kwica indi peptides myinshi, harimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi ikora ku mubyimba wa SLC6A19, umuyoboro wa amino acide udakumira, kandi biramenyekana ko ifitanye isano n'indwara y'umutima.
Nk'umushongi w'umura, ACE2 ikoreshwa nk'aho ingirabuzimafatizo y'ingenzi mu nsoro za virusi zimwe na zimwe za corona, zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituma habaho SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma habaho COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, poroteyine S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ifata ku ngirabuzimafatizo ACE2 bituma virusi na za enzymes zigera ku bice by'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo kandi zikagenda.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjira kandi bushaka kureba poroteyine ya S mu cyuma cyitwa TMPRSS2 cy'umunyamuryango, ubu kikaba ari umuti ukorwaho ubushakashatsi. Ibyo byatumye bamwe batekereza ko bishobora gufasha kurwanya indwara binyuze mu kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'inzobere n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura abantu, zasabye ko hakomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe yo kurwanya ACE na ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (USA), bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukoresha imiti ihagarika ACE byagabanyije indwara z'ibicurane ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abari bayigenzura.
Nanone kandi, ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibicurane, cyane cyane iyo mu bwonko no mu mutima, byari bimeze neza neza neza ku barwayi bavurwa indwara y'ibicurane ya ACE.
Gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bwa ACE byongeye gukoreshwa mu guhangana n'urupfu rufatanyije na pimo, kandi ingaruka zabyo zari nke ugereranyije n'ingaruka z'uburwayi bwa pimo.
Igiceri cya ACE2 (rhACE2) cy'umuntu giteganyijwe kuba umuti mushya wo kuvura indwara y'ibihaha by'indwara y'ubuhumekero iterwa na liposaccharide, kandi kigatuma habaho imikorere y'amaraso mu bihaha no kubura umwuka wa ogisijeni mu byana by'ingurube.
Ubuzima bw'igice cya kabiri cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera ku 10, kandi iminota 30 ni yo itangira gukora, uretse amasaha 24 y'akazi (igihe).
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe mu bantu badafite cyangwa bafite ingufu nyinshi za angiotensin II mu buryo bw'ibanze (RAS inhibitors).
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za mudasobwa zigendanwa zigamije gukurikirana cyangwa gufasha mu gushakisha abantu bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu urwaye.
Mu nzego zimwe na zimwe za leta no mu ntara, hari abantu benshi basabye ubufasha cyangwa babusaba, babifashijwemo n'ubufasha bwa leta.
Hari imiterere myinshi yashyizweho yo kubaka porogaramu zo gukurikirana abantu.
Hari impungenge z'ibanga cyane cyane ku byerekeye sisitemu zishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Uburyo bwo kutagira icyo umuntu akoraho cyane burimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona aho ari hafi y'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bizakora hamwe mu guhuza imikorere y'ibikoresho bikoresha Bluetooth muri sisitemu zikora za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu ya telefoni izatuma abaturage bamenya niba bahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Iyi porogaramu ikoreshwa muri Singapuru yitwa TraceTogether.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo muri ako gace, ikaba yarasohotse ari isoko ifunguye, kandi igahabwa leta. Muri Macédoine y'amajyaruguru, Bakayoko yatangije porogaramu ya StopKorona! ishingiye kuri Bluetooth yo gukurikirana ubukana bw'abantu banduye no gutanga ibisubizo byihuse.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Guhera ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu itegereje uruhushya rwo kuba mu bubiko bwa Google Play na Apple App Store.
"Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, Leta ya Amerika yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gushakisha abantu iri mu bihe bikomeye byo gutera imbere, kandi ko mu byumweru bike iri bube imaze gutangira gukoreshwa, porogaramu nk'iyo ikaba iteganyijwe muri Irlande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle Zélande byombi birimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether na protokoli ya BlueTrace ya Singapore. Uburusiya buteganya gutangiza porogaramu ya GeoFencing ku barwayi ba COVID-19 baba i Moscou, mu rwego rwo kwirinda kuva mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano, yavuze ibibazo byinshi birimo ingaruka mbi zishobora guterwa n'uburyo bwo gukoresha, hamwe n'uko ikoreshwa ry'ubu buryo rifite aho rihuriye n'abantu bake.
"Mu rwego rwo gukemura ikibazo cyo gukwirakwiza porogaramu za 'coronavirus' zangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku byiciro by'amashyirahamwe ashobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus mu bubiko bwa porogaramu, bigatuma byibandwa ku bigo byemewe cyangwa by'amazina azwi".
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye uburenganzira bwa muntu bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura ku buryo bwagutse hakoreshejwe porogaramu za virusi ya corona, cyane cyane ko ibikorwa remezo by'iperereza byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi, bishobora gusenyuka iyo iterabwoba rimaze gushira.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasabye ko hakurwaho ibyo bikorwa byo kugenzura.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani by'ibanze by'imishinga ya leta.
