Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda ko ryakongera urwikekwe n'ubwigenge;
Amakuru yose ashyirwa ahagaragara ku bantu ba gatatu agomba kumenyekana mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko;
hagomba kubaho ubuziranenge bwo kwirinda ihohoterwa no kurengera uburenganzira bw'abaturage;
"Kugira uruhare rwumvikana" ni ngombwa ku "bantu bose bafite uruhare rukomeye", harimo abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'itsinda ry'abashinzwe ubuzima. Ikigo cy'ubucungamari cy'u Budage (CCC) n'abanyamakuru (RSF) batanze urutonde rw'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi nta mbogamizi".
Iyo gahunda ya Google/Apple idakenewe kugira ngo ikemure ikibazo cyo gukurikirana abantu mu buryo buhoraho, bashobora gukuramo uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu ku bikoresho byabo.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana ahantu hashingiye ku muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, birinda ubushobozi bwo gukuramo porogaramu no gukumira gukurikirana.
Israel yemeje ikoreshwa ry'ikoranabuhanga mu gukurikirana abantu.
Ibisubizo bishingiye kuri interineti byo kugera ku makuru mu karere kahumye bishobora kugira ibibazo.
Icyakora, sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru ntizigomba kugira uburenganzira bwo kubona amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari, hari sisitemu nyinshi zo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite zakoreweho zikoresha seriveri nkuru gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice kiri hasi).
